the circumstances...

00:20:38.197 --> 00:20:40.157 position:50% align:center
We don't really have
the time to fight.

00:20:40.240 --> 00:20:42.034 position:50% align:center
So it's not that big of a deal.

00:20:42.117 --> 00:20:46.288 position:50% align:center
[KAKUSHI]
Hm... Then why'd I get beat up?

00:20:46.371 --> 00:20:50.792 position:50% align:center
[exhales] It's super cold out
tonight. Isn't it, Daddy?

00:20:50.876 --> 00:20:53.295 position:50% align:center
Yeah. It sure is.

00:20:53.378 --> 00:20:56.173 position:50% align:center
Hey, wait. Where is your coat?

00:20:56.256 --> 00:21:02.179 position:50% align:center
[SATSUKI hums] My new coat
is so warm and fluffy!

00:21:02.262 --> 00:21:03.305 position:50% align:center
[KAKUSHI]
That bastard.

00:21:03.388 --> 00:21:05.432 position:50% align:center
Wanna use my scarf? You can.

00:21:05.516 --> 00:21:07.392 position:50% align:center
That's very sweet,
but I'll be okay.

00:21:07.476 --> 00:21:09.937 position:50% align:center
So, anyway. Did you have
lots of fun tonight?

00:21:10.020 --> 00:21:12.648 position:50% align:center
Uh-huh! The Cinderella
was amazing!

00:21:12.731 --> 00:21:16.985 position:50% align:center
It was so big! And sparkly!
Kinda like diamonds!

00:21:17.069 --> 00:21:18.320 position:50% align:center
I see.

00:21:18.403 --> 00:21:19.446 position:50% align:center
[HIME]
Uh?

00:21:19.530 --> 00:21:20.322 position:50% align:center
What?

00:21:20.405 --> 00:21:22.824 position:50% align:center
Daddy. What's that?

00:21:24.743 --> 00:21:29.122 position:50% align:center
[HIME] Oh, wow!
Check out this Cinderella!

00:21:29.206 --> 00:21:32.793 position:50% align:center
It's more like a
super-Cinderella! Heh.

00:21:34.253 --> 00:21:36.046 position:50% align:center
[KAKUSHI chuckles]

00:21:36.129 --> 00:21:39.883 position:50% align:center
[KAKUSHI] I want to protect that
smile. So I'll keep it a secret.

00:21:39.967 --> 00:21:43.136 position:50% align:center
I won't let her find out
that I'm a manga artist.

00:21:54.481 --> 00:21:56.149 position:50% align:center
Welcome, sir.

00:22:02.322 --> 00:22:04.449 position:50% align:center
That's 800 yen.

00:22:09.746 --> 00:22:11.665 position:50% align:center
[AOGU]
Thank you very much.

00:22:14.334 --> 00:22:17.004 position:50% align:center
[AOGU]
Yeah, right. What a lie.

00:23:47.803 --> 00:23:49.388 position:50% align:center
[SATSUKI]
Hold on! Are you gonna die?

00:23:49.471 --> 00:23:51.473 position:50% align:center
[ICHIKO] Why don't we all
try writing a new prayer?

00:23:51.557 --> 00:23:53.016 position:50% align:center
One to help your dad get better?

00:23:53.100 --> 00:23:54.268 position:50% align:center
[KAKUSHI]
Manga artists who go overseas

00:23:54.351 --> 00:23:56.854 position:50% align:center
during New Years
are total jerk wads!